"{\"uid\": \"freepressjournal.in-pune-punit-balan-group-rewards-olympic-bronze-medalist-swapnil-kusale-with-11-lakh\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Punit Balan Group (PBG) has rewarded Olympic Bronze Medalist Swapnil Kusale with Rs 11 lakh for his outstanding performance.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6, \"end\": 11, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sir_Balin\", \"score\": 0.841882049005578, \"rank\": 0.12892638021464145, \"text\": \"Balan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sir_Balin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sir_Balin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PBG President and young entrepreneur, Punit Balan, presented the reward cheque to Swapnil on Monday, September 9.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 238, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 169, \"end\": 174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sir_Balin\", \"score\": 0.841882049005578, \"rank\": 0.12892638021464145, \"text\": \"Balan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sir_Balin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sir_Balin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Swapnil, hailing from Kolhapur, won the bronze medal in the 50-metre rifle shooting (three-position) event at the Paris Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 240, \"to\": 374, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 262, \"end\": 270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kolhapur\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.649776222912388e-17, \"text\": \"Kolhapur\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kolhapur\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kolhapur\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He became the second player from Maharashtra to win an individual medal at the Olympics, following Khashaba Jadhav, who earned a bronze in wrestling at the 1952 Olympics.\", \"from\": 375, \"to\": 545, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 408, \"end\": 419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maharashtra\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.5318967065765132e-13, \"text\": \"Maharashtra\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maharashtra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maharashtra\"}, {\"begin\": 474, \"end\": 489, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/K._D._Jadhav\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Khashaba Jadhav\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/K._D._Jadhav\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/K._D._Jadhav\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Recognizing Swapnil's achievement, Punit Balan announced the Rs 11 lakh reward.\", \"from\": 547, \"to\": 626, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 588, \"end\": 593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sir_Balin\", \"score\": 0.841882049005578, \"rank\": 0.12892638021464145, \"text\": \"Balan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sir_Balin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sir_Balin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Swapnil was also given the honor of performing the 'Aarti' at the Shrimant Bhausaheb Rangari Ganpati on the same day.\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 744, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Later, Punit Balan handed over the cheque to him.\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 794, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Expressing his gratitude, Swapnil said, \\\"I am a devout Ganesh follower, and with Bappa's blessings, I was able to win the bronze medal.\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 931, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is a privilege to perform the 'Aarti' of Shrimant Bhausaheb Rangari Ganpati.\\\"\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 1012, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 976, \"end\": 984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baby_shower\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shrimant\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baby_shower\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baby_shower\"}, {\"begin\": 1003, \"end\": 1010, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ganesha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ganpati\", \"types\": [\"Q24229398\", \"Q178885\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ganesha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ganesha\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PBG has been known for supporting emerging and talented athletes through financial aid, which has been widely appreciated by the public.\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1150, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Punit Balan, speaking at the event, praised Swapnil's accomplishment, stating, \\\"Swapnil has not only made Maharashtra proud but also the entire country.\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1304, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1158, \"end\": 1163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sir_Balin\", \"score\": 0.841882049005578, \"rank\": 0.12892638021464145, \"text\": \"Balan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sir_Balin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sir_Balin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are many athletes like him who need nurturing, and Punit Balan Group is committed to encouraging such talents.\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1421, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1368, \"end\": 1373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sir_Balin\", \"score\": 0.841882049005578, \"rank\": 0.12892638021464145, \"text\": \"Balan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sir_Balin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sir_Balin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am confident that Swapnil will win the gold medal in the future.\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1488, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On behalf of the Shrimant Bhausaheb Rangari Trust and all Ganesh devotees, I wish him the best.\\\"\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1585, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1506, \"end\": 1514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baby_shower\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.9588717418979264e-18, \"text\": \"Shrimant\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baby_shower\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baby_shower\"}, {\"begin\": 1547, \"end\": 1553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ganesha\"